reviewText: Hello. I gave this five stars because I know and like the movie. I bought from a seller in the USA, thinking I was safe as far as DVD Region was concerned. But, NOOO! Wrong region! My bad; NOT sellers! Just be careful. If not you'll be stuck with a box w/a good movie in it, that you can watch in Australia next time you go! Your best bet might be to git the 'A Fairly Odd Movie' trilogy. Ta!
